keyFromHash(String) - Method in class RBT.Search
Attempt to find plain-text key that corresponds to hash provided by user.
Starting from the far right (end) chain, we work our way towards the front of the chain, one step at a time, running each location in the chain through hashToHashStep(), and check the resulting hash for a match against searchHash.
